{"tid":2366742,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"世衞專家抵武漢　計劃留一個月 希望調查揭示病毒起源新細節","createTime":"2021-01-14T18:54:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T13:34:00.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"8d7d119ae680d6390907630bc646ab8ef9620e93","tid":2366742,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T18:54:51.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎爆發逾一年後，負責調查病毒起源的世衞專家組昨日終於抵達最早發現病毒的湖北武漢。世衞專家組從新加坡出發，昨早11時飛抵當地。當中越南生物學家阮洪（Hung Nguyen）表示，計劃於當地停留一個月，希望調查能揭示病毒起源的新細節。兩名世衞專家組成員在新加坡登機前被檢測出對病毒呈陽性，被中方拒絕登機。<br />\n<br />\n世衞證實，15名來自不同國家的專家從本國出發前已接受檢測，全部呈陰性；抵達新加坡後再測試，所有人的聚合酶連鎖反應都呈陰性，惟其中兩人免疫球蛋白M（IgM）測試呈陽性。目前抵達武漢的專家為13人。<br />\n<br />\n阮洪出發前指，隔離14日後專家組會有兩周時間調查，包括訪問當地研究機構、醫院、海鮮市場的相關人士。他稱，「我的理解是，團隊在獲取訊息時實際上是沒有限制的」；他希望在這次考察中找到新的細節。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210115/N5HZ7X4J2VF3NDTJAEBGVFL4HI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210115%2FN5HZ7X4J2VF3NDTJAEBGVFL4HI%2F&d=qXcR1A%2FTALq%2FhnoNE0cJVbnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=1660b220\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210115%2FN5HZ7X4J2VF3NDTJAEBGVFL4HI%2F&h=c9054fb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210115/N5HZ7X4J2VF3NDTJAEBGVFL4HI/</a>"},{"pid":"c9fe9b14232c469f2815d3e24fed333915ddc0ee","tid":2366742,"uid":605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T18:55:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"923bff2dae6447229460f5f2f89ab98d082d0c6a","tid":2366742,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T18:56:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdf6aa3ada0e3eab064291789d4f6fe6d9bc7ab3","ti